{"lastModified":1748871171501,"uri":"c::7819307041::vessel::bdf51bb0-3a4f-11f0-a87f-3164d6f20974","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nSHARING / WELL-BEING\n\nLiving spaces are privileged, filled with voluptuous calm for exceptional getaways.\n\nERGONOMIC DESIGN / REFINEMENT\n\nA contemporary and sophisticated interior design, with a customisable layout to bring your dream sailboat to life.\n\nWELCOMING / SOPHISTICATED\n\nWith a sensation of tranquility, you feel transported from the moment you step aboard the Jeanneau Yachts 54. The generous interior opens onto infinite space, conducive to relaxation.\n\nWith a sensation of power born of majestic lines, the world of large yachts calls you to experience unforgettable moments in complete serenity.\n\nDesigned to Live in Communion with the Sea\n\nA yacht with majestic lines, designed to cut through the waves and to travel the world, the Jean-neau Yachts 54, in keeping with the spirit of the line, features exterior living spaces designed to enable you to freely enjoy all the pleasures of life on the water. The dedicated space for the helmsman and for handling all controls is located in the aft cockpit: the helm, the engine, the bow thruster, the sheets of the mainsail and genoa… leaving the space clear for the generous cockpit dining area, surrounded by living areas dedicated for relaxation: sun loungers located to either side of the companionway, and at anchor, a recessed sundeck on the forward deck, and two more on the swim platform.\n\nUnmatched Equipment and Comfort on Board\n\nThe interior of this sailboat, filled with luxurious details and ideal for relaxation, is very well equipped, notably in the galley, and features great volumes of storage space and a generous and enjoyable owner’s cabin, with: a large berth, easy flow of movement, contemporary design, and windows in the hull enabling you to comfortably read a book with a view of the sea. With the Jeanneau Yachts 54, each moment approaches perfection.","blueprint":{"name":"OUR LADY","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::bdf51bb0-3a4f-11f0-a87f-3164d6f20974::assets::7fd8ec10-3a51-11f0-bab0-3ff23b9dbec8/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bdf51bb0-3a4f-11f0-a87f-3164d6f20974::assets::7fa4bcb0-3a51-11f0-bab0-3ff23b9dbec8/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bdf51bb0-3a4f-11f0-a87f-3164d6f20974::assets::7fcba5a0-3a51-11f0-bab0-3ff23b9dbec8/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bdf51bb0-3a4f-11f0-a87f-3164d6f20974::assets::7fb5d3b0-3a51-11f0-bab0-3ff23b9dbec8/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bdf51bb0-3a4f-11f0-a87f-3164d6f20974::assets::7fa61c40-3a51-11f0-bab0-3ff23b9dbec8/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bdf51bb0-3a4f-11f0-a87f-3164d6f20974::assets::7fa46e91-3a51-11f0-bab0-3ff23b9dbec8/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bdf51bb0-3a4f-11f0-a87f-3164d6f20974::assets::7fa7f100-3a51-11f0-bab0-3ff23b9dbec8/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bdf51bb0-3a4f-11f0-a87f-3164d6f20974::assets::7fa46e90-3a51-11f0-bab0-3ff23b9dbec8/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bdf51bb0-3a4f-11f0-a87f-3164d6f20974::assets::7fc7ae00-3a51-11f0-bab0-3ff23b9dbec8/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bdf51bb0-3a4f-11f0-a87f-3164d6f20974::assets::7fa50ad0-3a51-11f0-bab0-3ff23b9dbec8/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bdf51bb0-3a4f-11f0-a87f-3164d6f20974::assets::7fa77bd0-3a51-11f0-bab0-3ff23b9dbec8/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bdf51bb0-3a4f-11f0-a87f-3164d6f20974::assets::7fa3d250-3a51-11f0-bab0-3ff23b9dbec8/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::bdf51bb0-3a4f-11f0-a87f-3164d6f20974::assets::7fa4e3c0-3a51-11f0-bab0-3ff23b9dbec8/{imageVariant}"],"make":"Jeanneau","model":"Jeanneau 54","sleeps":12,"basePort":{"uri":"a::place::efcafd20-b3ed-11ed-bad5-325096b39f47","name":"Lefkada","coordinates":{"latitude":38.83492998236817,"longitude":20.71116234489464},"country"